Well, this feels like the familiar usual one

60
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:51,100
もう見た目からしてね
just from the look of it

61
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:54,000
匂いも、なんかいつも馴染んでいる牛丼な気がしますね
The smell too, it feels like the beef bowl I'm always familiar with

62
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,200
いろは様も分かります？
Do you know too, Iroha-sama?

63
